A new species of Schlettererius Ashmead from China, with a key to the species (Hymenoptera, Stephanidae)A new species of Schlettererius Ashmead, 1900, S. chundanae sp. n., is described and illustrated from China. The other East Palaearctic species, S. determinatorius Madl, 1991, is redescribed and illustrated, the first host record is given and it is newly reported from China. A key to the species of the genus Schlettererius is included.